snippet.title: In Search of Light - Full gameplay
snippet.description:
Play the Game - https://angrykid.itch.io/in-search-of-light

In search of Light - is an adventure game in which you are playing as an outcast engineer living in a dystopian future.

Was made during Global Game Jam 2020 at Kyiv location. Global Game Jam page - https://globalgamejam.org/2020/games/search-light-9
